      <td>Non-Turing-complete, linear-time, designed to embed. <strong>protovalidate</strong> proves it at v1.0 scale across 5 languages with <em>no codegen</em>. Cost: each target embeds/transpiles a CEL evaluator. <strong>The reference design.</strong></td>
    </tr>
