      <td>Survives JSON-Schema codegen, but <strong>cannot express value-comparison cross-field</strong> (<code>endDate &gt; startDate</code>). <code>dependentRequired</code> = property-presence only; nested <code>if/then/else</code> under <code>allOf</code> gets "very messy." Covers the easy third of cross-field, not the hard two-thirds.</td>
